  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a Besu user, I want to be able to upgrade Besu version while in the middle of fastsync. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* be able to stop and upgrade Besu to new version in the middle of fast sync\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Start fastsync on old version of Besu\r\n2. Stop Besu before the fast sync world state download finishes\r\n3. Upgrade to the latest Besu commit\r\n4. Start Besu\r\n\r\n**Frequency:** [What percentage of the time does it occur?]\r\n* The problem always happens, but may be not visible because missing world state nodes are not in use yet.",
